  <main class="container pub">
    <header class="pub-header">
      <h1>HospiTALK</h1>
    </header>
    <hr class="rule">

    <img src="/assets/portfolio/hospitalk.jpg" alt="HospiTALK project mockup" style="width:100%; border-radius:16px; margin:20px 0;">

    <p class="serif">
      HospiTALK is a flexible scheduling platform co-developed with Amsterdam UMC to improve autonomy, transparency, 
      and coordination in clinical department staff scheduling.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
      Nurses often experience inflexible shift structures and limited visibility into scheduling decisions.
      This project reimagined the daily planning process to give staff more control while maintaining 
      operational efficiency.
    </p>

    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Through shadowing sessions, co-design workshops, and workflow mapping, 
      we identified systemic barriers and prototyped a digital tool integrating both personal preferences 
      and task needs.
    </p>

    <img src="/assets/portfolio/hospitalk-workflow.jpg" alt="Workflow mapping" style="width:100%; border-radius:12px; margin:16px 0;">

    <h2>Outcome</h2>
    <p>
      The resulting platform prototype allows staff to negotiate shifts collaboratively 
      and visualize task distributions, aligning organizational needs with individual autonomy.
    </p>

    <hr class="rule">

